    "4008917": {
        "Desc": "Complete the first round of the Test of Courage",
        "Step": "You decided to join Kazuha in the first round. What challenges will you encounter along the way?",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Look, everyone. Isn't this the Dango Milk we are searching for?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "And there's a scarecrow beside it. Strange... What is that doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well, it doesn't matter now! Since we found the Dango Milk, then we must be the first ones here, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But there's no way we can carry back so much Dango Milk. Why don't we drink some to lighten the load a little?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon could use a sip... Whaa!!! The scarecrow stood up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "It appears to be guarding the Dango Milk here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You mean, it's watching if we touch the Dango Milk? Uh, don't worry, P—Paimon didn't even touch it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's try not to scare ourselves."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're getting scared over nothing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, maybe you're right, Paimon will try to calm down... Let's try some together!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You drink some Dango Milk with Ayaka..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Mmm, tastes great!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Indeed. Any fears I had a moment ago seem to have been dissipated by the Dango Milk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "And now that I look around, this is Chinju Forest as I have always known it. After making it here, it doesn't seem nearly as frightening."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "My brother once said that fear stems from one's heart, and if your heart is at peace, then fear naturally dissipates. Now I understand what he meant."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "But fear is not entirely bad... Although I've been scared a few times, I still feel happy now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "I would like to continue walking through the forest for a while. Will you accompany me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think I saw someone I know just now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Ah, I see. Well, I shall continue walking while you go greet your friend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kamisato Ayaka",
                    "T": "Don't worry. Now that I've experienced the event once already, I won't be easily frightened. I'll see you later. Have a lovely chat with your friend."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
